title: Telegram for b1mt
body: Currently we are using `1Milliontoken` and `The Millionaire Club` telegram groups for `1mt` and `b1mt`.  For `b1mt` we have different purpose than `1mt`, with this coin will not be any giveaway, rain, etc... We want that the holders invest providing liquidity to pools, using for Defi projects, NFT market, gambling etc... We realized that the majority of the users in `1Milliontoken` group are not interesting in the project, only in getting free coins without invest, and the group `The Millionaire Club` we doubt its utility because of this we can do one of the next options:
choices: Use The Millionaire Club for b1m
Create a new group for b1mt
